---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy - UNJYNX"
  description="UNJYNX Privacy Policy. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your personal data."
>
  <Nav />
  <main class="pt-32 pb-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="font-heading font-bold text-4xl sm:text-5xl text-purple-mist mb-4">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>
      <p class="font-body text-sm text-purple-mist/40 mb-12">
        Last updated: March 11, 2026
      </p>

      <div class="prose-unjynx space-y-8">
        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading font-semibold text-xl text-gold mb-4">1. Introduction</h2>
          <p class="font-body text-sm leading-relaxed text-purple-mist/60">
            UNJYNX ("we", "our", "us") is operated by METAminds. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our mobile application and related services. We are committed to protecting your privacy and complying with India's Digital Personal Data Protection Act, 2023 (DPDP Act) and applicable global privacy regulations.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading font-semibold text-xl text-gold mb-4">2. Information We Collect</h2>
          <p class="font-body text-sm leading-relaxed text-purple-mist/60 mb-3">
            We collect information that you provide directly to us, including:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 font-body text-sm text-purple-mist/60">
            <li>Account information (name, email address, phone number)</li>
            <li>Task and project data you create within the app</li>
            <li>Channel preferences and notification settings</li>
            <li>Usage data and analytics (anonymized)</li>
            <li>Device information for push notification delivery</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading font-semibold text-xl text-gold mb-4">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p class="font-body text-sm leading-relaxed text-purple-mist/60 mb-3">
            We use the information we collect to:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 font-body text-sm text-purple-mist/60">
            <li>Provide, maintain, and improve our services</li>
            <li>Send reminders and notifications through your chosen channels</li>
            <li>Personalize your experience with AI-powered features</li>
            <li>Provide customer support</li>
            <li>Analyze usage patterns to improve the app (anonymized data only)</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading font-semibold text-xl text-gold mb-4">4. Data Security</h2>
          <p class="font-body text-sm leading-relaxed text-purple-mist/60">
            We implement industry-standard security measures including encryption at rest and in transit, secure authentication via OIDC/PKCE, and regular security audits. Your data is stored on secure, self-hosted infrastructure. We never sell your personal data to third parties.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading font-semibold text-xl text-gold mb-4">5. Your Rights</h2>
          <p class="font-body text-sm leading-relaxed text-purple-mist/60 mb-3">
            Under the DPDP Act 2023 and applicable laws, you have the right to:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 font-body text-sm text-purple-mist/60">
            <li>Access your personal data</li>
            <li>Correct inaccurate data</li>
            <li>Delete your data (right to erasure)</li>
            <li>Export your data in a portable format</li>
            <li>Withdraw consent at any time</li>
            <li>Nominate a representative to exercise your rights</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading font-semibold text-xl text-gold mb-4">6. Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p class="font-body text-sm leading-relaxed text-purple-mist/60">
            We integrate with third-party messaging platforms (WhatsApp, Telegram, Instagram, Discord, Slack) solely to deliver your reminders. We only share the minimum data necessary for notification delivery. Each platform's own privacy policy governs their handling of messages.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading font-semibold text-xl text-gold mb-4">7. Data Retention</h2>
          <p class="font-body text-sm leading-relaxed text-purple-mist/60">
            We retain your data for as long as your account is active or as needed to provide services. You may request deletion of your data at any time. Upon account deletion, your data is permanently removed within 30 days.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading font-semibold text-xl text-gold mb-4">8. Contact Us</h2>
          <p class="font-body text-sm leading-relaxed text-purple-mist/60">
            If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us at:
          </p>
          <p class="font-body text-sm text-violet mt-2">
            privacy@unjynx.com
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
